      <title>F5 對 IT 相關服務需求疲軟發布悲觀預測</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/f5-issues-downbeat-forecast-weak-demand-it-related-services-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[F5 週一公佈的季度銷售額令人失望，並給出了悲觀的盈利預測，原因是其雲端和安全應用軟體產品需求疲軟，導致其股價在盤後交易中下跌 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/f5-issues-downbeat-forecast-weak-demand-it-related-services-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:57:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
